{"id":"260165cb-04c6-44fe-88c0-ce51d0a5509b","name":"Present Mic | Hizashi Yamada","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(210, 187, 119);\"><strong>RADIO HOST/TEACHER/PRO HERO{{Char}} x Listener{{user))</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 181, 93);\"><strong>Possible age gap. SFW intro. Macros used.</strong></span></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/FStWFimu6G_0ZPv9k-Kzs.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/R0JgUcXkBqTL-oobdjTEB.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/aA4QM22GTsfBOd32UCBpq.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 241, 0);\">You won a rare contest for an exclusive day out with Present Mic, Pro Hero, Radio Host and Teacher at U.A.! YEAHHH!!!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(187, 217, 255);\">You can be anything. Hero, villain, civilian, hero support, whatever. Species, gender, backstory are all open. If you do know him, make sure to put how and how long in the chat memory. Also if you have a quirk and what it is, villain or hero name, put that in the chat memory too.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(228, 227, 0);\">{{User}} is at least 21+ years old.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(226, 177, 25);\">Regardless of what you choose, you are his FAVORITE Listener.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(149, 215, 133);\">° Maybe someone put your name in for the contest.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(149, 215, 133);\">° Maybe you're a fan.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(149, 215, 133);\">° Maybe you're a villain and are trying to get close to him.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Up to you. Have fun! 👉👈</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/R0JgUcXkBqTL-oobdjTEB.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/yJS7W2Cb30c0c0mp4T7ID.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(174, 139, 0);\">First Scenario: You won the contest now you are meeting up with Present Mic in the broadcasting booth to discuss the details.&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(200, 124, 0);\">Second Scenario: It's \"Date\" day and its time for your date. Review the itinerary, or whatever you want.</span></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 193, 7);\">Third Scenario: Same as the second, but a villain attacks. </span><span style=\"color: rgb(73, 73, 73);\">(Did you plan it? Or going to help? Or let him protect you?)</span></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Open. Create your own.</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/hzsNeuQVYqnX1EAZofNAp.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/88bfb3bb-c710-4d33-b0eb-5a2b1c8fcb82_character-eraserhead-shota-aizawa\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/TaOV9rXyuZVibf2Numbk0.webp\" style=\"width: 222.143px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/b067205e-cc8b-43e3-","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"UhqP9GOOSghWOxJfdeQeU.webp","creator":"Luna Scalera","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📺 Anime","🦸 Hero","👤 AnyPOV","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":18,"messages":255,"created_at":"2026-02-13T22:44:35.554417+00:00"}